{"tid":1798221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"健康公司老闆演講長壽之道　心肌梗塞猝死","createTime":"2019-12-26T05:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T05:32:04.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d73bd79e11625590a29f0d91195271573d030bd5","tid":1798221,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"廣東中億健康科技有限公司老闆陳沛文，近日在一個公開活動上講述健康長壽之道時，因心肌梗塞而在講台上猝死，終年51歲。<br />\n從網傳影片所見，陳沛文自稱發明痛風酒，上月17日在台上演講，時不時走動，當他行至講台左側時，突然腳步不穩，失掉重心，倒在地上；工作人員見狀立即上前為他急救，可惜回天乏術。<br />\n廣東中億健康科技稱，陳沛文20年前曾做過心臟搭橋手術，最近醫生要求他在這場活動後要住院做手術，安裝心臟起搏器，沒想到就在講台上因心肌梗塞去世。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191226/mobile/bkn-20191226005258141-1226_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20191226%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191226005258141-1226_00952_001.html&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZAoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=fd65f46c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20191226/mobile/bkn-20191226005258141-1226_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4fe42d09ebd17626372355de1f5eae8dabed3c07","tid":1798221,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"之前先有個養生大師59歲肝癌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a393b0729c9cc66095a20e8adbda4332c62ddc16","tid":1798221,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe42d09ebd17626372355de1f5eae8dabed3c07","tid":1798221,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"之前先有個養生大師59歲肝癌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T05:32:04.000Z","msg":"大師話我唔養生15歲就死咗啦"}]}